      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 scoping guidance. Analyst qualifications are noted in project records but formal use-error assessment is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
